## Lock File

Lock file: `yarn.lock`

> Always commit the lock file. Never manually edit it.

## Rules

1. Add new dependencies through the package manager — never edit manifests manually
2. Prefer well-maintained, actively developed libraries
3. Keep dev dependencies separate from production dependencies
4. Run security audits regularly (`npm audit`, `pip-audit`, etc.)
